videos.description: Kevin Johnson hits his third 3-pointer of the half to put his team up 2
videos.headline: Kevin Johnson drains a three from the top of the key

videos.description: Cincinnati runs the court quickly in transition, with Tre Scott getting the ball and finishing at the rim for a two-handed flush.
videos.headline: Cinci's Tre Scott throws it down in transition

videos.description: Cincy's Troy Caupain drains a 3-pointer, Sterling Brown responds for SMU
videos.headline: Cincy's Troy Caupain drains a 3-pointer, Sterling Brown responds for SMU

videos.description: Gary Clark catches the ball under the rim and throws it down
videos.headline: Gary Clark throws down the two-handed jam with authority

videos.description: SMU scoops up the loose ball and Ben Moore throws it down
videos.headline: SMU scoops up the loose ball and Ben Moore throws it down

videos.description: SMU loses track of Cincy's Gary Clark and looks on as he throws down a dunk.
videos.headline: Clark left open again, throws down another ferocious jam

videos.description: Jarrey Foster knocks down 3-pointer from the wing to cut Cincy lead to 2
videos.headline: Jarrey Foster knocks down 3-pointer from the wing to cut Cincy lead to 2

videos.description: Semi Ojeleye catches the lob and dunks it down to cut the Cincy lead to 3
videos.headline: Semi Ojeleye catches the lob and dunks it down to cut the Cincy lead to 3

videos.description: Jarrey Foster buries a clutch 3-pointer from the wing to cut the SMU deficit to 2 with just over a minute to play
videos.headline: Jarrey Foster buries a clutch 3-pointer from the wing
